      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-09T19:00:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t know of another way to do it, unless there\u0027s a clever way to propagate using contexts.  Added a mutex to prevent concurrent writes.",
      "parentUuid": "3618850b_096e8c98",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 64,
        "startChar": 4,
